com.facebook.buck.core.rules.analysis.impl

Class RuleAnalysisTransformer

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.facebook.buck.core.rules.analysis.impl.RuleAnalysisTransformer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GraphTransformer<RuleAnalysisKey,RuleAnalysisResult>

    public class RuleAnalysisTransformer
extends Object
implements GraphTransformer<RuleAnalysisKey,RuleAnalysisResult>
    The GraphTransformer for performing the target graph to provider and action graph transformation.

    This represents the stage of Buck where the TargetGraph is transformed into the Provider graph, along with the registered Actions.
